        <p data-i18n="about.p1">
          Psychography was born as a band project in 2020 in the city of Buenos&nbsp;Aires, Argentina, founded by Yanina&nbsp;Islas (Vocals). Their songs reflect a blend of different metal subgenres, creating a progressive-tinged atmosphere that moves between Metalcore and Thall.
        </p>
        <p data-i18n-html="about.p2">
          With five singles released, a feature on <em>Under&nbsp;The&nbsp;Wing</em> by Dan&nbsp;Sugarman (Ice&nbsp;Nine&nbsp;Kills), and being the first Argentine band on the Arson&nbsp;Theory distributor, Psychography has consolidated its sonic identity.
        </p>
        <p data-i18n-html="about.p3">
          In 2026 they premiered the official music video for <em>Screams&nbsp;In&nbsp;The&nbsp;Mind</em>.
        </p>

